These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
City: nizza, prague
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, eggplant
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
6. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Flower         | lily   | bellflower     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | superhero  |
| City   | prague | nizza |
| Food           | grapefruit      | eggplant     |
| Sport     | snowboarding    | cycling   |

