.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, soccer
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman
City: new-york, san-francisco
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold
2 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | water-polo    | soccer |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Cigar           | dannemann | chaman  |
| City   | san-francisco            | new-york    |
| Flower   | zinnia     | marigold   |
| Pet           | lizard         | mouse    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

