The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, r&b
2 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, sailing
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, tram
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
3. the fan of pop is the person who likes orange##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating peach##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food         | peach  | pumpkin    |
| Beverage           | milk       | cola    |
| Color   | orange | red    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b |
